Generic single-database configuration.

## Set-up

See requirements file. If you encounter `Marshmallow` errors, ensure marshmallow-flask is installed.

`APP_CONFIG_FILE` must be set in your environment variables. It should point to whichever configuration you need (prod, test, dev, etc).

